Package imp.core.model.loop

Contains all classes related to kinematic loops.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Loop
    Loop data structure The loop is a list of joints in the order they are found in the loop
    LoopCloser
    This class is used to close all of the loops in a model.
    LoopFinder
    This class is used to find the kinematic loops.
    LoopVariable
    This class is used in loop closure to keep all data for a changed joint.
